{% comment %}
============================================================
BLOQUE: Productos Destacados — Home (Quiet Luxury)
Fuente de datos: 100% Shopify en vivo (all_products), NO hardcodeado.
Pega este bloque dentro de templates/index.liquid (o inclúyelo ahí con
{% render 'home-productos-destacados' %} si lo mueves a /snippets).

CÓMO ESCALAR:
Para agregar un producto nuevo al home, solo añade su handle a la lista
`product_handles` de abajo. El handle es el slug de la URL del producto
en Shopify (ej: miproducto.myshopify.com/products/ESTE-ES-EL-HANDLE).
No hay que tocar nada más: precio, imágenes, descripción, stock y
disponibilidad se leen en vivo desde Shopify en cada carga de página.

Handles activos ahora mismo (auditados vía conector Shopify, 2026-07-12):
  - sandalias-planas-impermeables-antideslizantes  ($34.95, 27 variantes)
  - dispositivo-facial-de-microcorriente            ($24.95, 1 variante)
============================================================
{% endcomment %}

<section class="ql-home-products" id="productos-destacados">
  <style>
    .ql-home-products {
      --ql-bg: #faf8f5;
      --ql-ink: #1c1a17;
      --ql-muted: #6f6a62;
      --ql-line: #e4ded4;
      --ql-accent: #1c1a17;
      background: var(--ql-bg);
      padding: 48px 16px;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .ql-home-products__header {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto 32px;
    }
    .ql-home-products__header h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      color: var(--ql-ink);
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .ql-home-products__header p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--ql-muted);
      margin: 0;
    }
    .ql-home-products__grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .ql-card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--ql-line);
      border-radius: 4px;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .ql-card__media {
      position: relative;
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #f1efe9;
    }
    .ql-card__img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }
    .ql-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: 12px;
      left: 12px;
      background: var(--ql-ink);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
    .ql-card__body {
      padding: 18px 16px 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .ql-card__title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--ql-ink);
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }
    .ql-card__desc {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--ql-muted);
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .ql-card__price {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .ql-price {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--ql-ink);
    }
    .ql-price--compare {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--ql-muted);
      text-decoration: line-through;
    }
    .ql-selectors {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .ql-select-label {
      flex: 1 1 120px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--ql-muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }
    .ql-select {
      padding: 8px 10px;
      border: 1px solid var(--ql-line);
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--ql-ink);
      background: #fff;
    }
    .ql-btn-add {
      margin-top: 6px;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 13px 16px;
      background: var(--ql-accent);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .ql-btn-add:active { opacity: 0.85; }
    .ql-btn-add--disabled,
    .ql-btn-add:disabled {
      background: #cfc9bd;
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }

    @media (min-width: 700px) {
      .ql-home-products__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
      .ql-home-products__header h2 { font-size: 26px; }
    }
    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
      .ql-home-products__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
      .ql-home-products { padding: 64px 24px; }
    }
  </style>

  <div class="ql-home-products__header">
    <h2>Selección de la temporada</h2>
    <p>Piezas elegidas, calidad garantizada.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="ql-home-products__grid">
    {% assign product_handles = "sandalias-planas-impermeables-antideslizantes,dispositivo-facial-de-microcorriente" | split: "," %}
    {% for handle in product_handles %}
      {% assign product = all_products[handle] %}
      {% if product != empty %}
        <article class="ql-card" data-product-id="{{ product.id }}">
          <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="ql-card__media">
            <img
              class="ql-card__img"
              src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
              alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | default: product.title | escape }}"
              width="800"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            >
            {% if product.compare_at_price > product.price %}
              <span class="ql-badge">Oferta</span>
            {% endif %}
          </a>

          <div class="ql-card__body">
            <h3 class="ql-card__title">{{ product.title }}</h3>
            <p class="ql-card__desc">{{ product.description | strip_html | truncate: 100 }}</p>

            <div class="ql-card__price">
              <span class="ql-price">{{ product.price | money }}</span>
              {% if product.compare_at_price > product.price %}
                <span class="ql-price--compare">{{ product.compare_at_price | money }}</span>
              {% endif %}
            </div>

            <form method="post" action="/cart/add" class="ql-card__form" data-product-form>
              {% if product.options_with_values.size > 0 and product.variants.size > 1 %}
                <div class="ql-selectors">
                  {% for option in product.options_with_values %}
                    <label class="ql-select-label">
                      {{ option.name }}
                      <select class="ql-select" data-option-index="{{ forloop.index0 }}">
                        {% for value in option.values %}
                          <option value="{{ value | escape }}">{{ value }}</option>
                        {% endfor %}
                      </select>
                    </label>
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
              {% endif %}

              <input
                type="hidden"
                name="id"
                value="{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}"
                data-variant-id-input
              >

              <script type="application/json" data-variant-map>
                {
                  {% for variant in product.variants %}
                    "{{ variant.options | join: ' / ' }}": {
                      "id": {{ variant.id }},
                      "available": {{ variant.available }}
                    }{% unless forloop.last %},{% endunless %}
                  {% endfor %}
                }
              </script>

              <button type="submit" class="ql-btn-add" {% unless product.available %}disabled{% endunless %}>
                {% if product.available %}Agregar al carrito{% else %}Agotado{% endif %}
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </article>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

{% comment %}
  Script vanilla, sin librerías externas (~1kb). Solo sincroniza los
  <select> de color/talla con el ID de variante real de Shopify antes
  de enviar el formulario a /cart/add.
{% endcomment %}
<script defer>
(function () {
  document.querySelectorAll('[data-product-form]').forEach(function (form) {
    var mapEl = form.querySelector('[data-variant-map]');
    if (!mapEl) return;
    var variantMap = JSON.parse(mapEl.textContent);
    var selects = form.querySelectorAll('.ql-select');
    var hiddenInput = form.querySelector('[data-variant-id-input]');
    var btn = form.querySelector('.ql-btn-add');
    if (!selects.length || !hiddenInput) return;

    function updateVariant() {
      var key = Array.prototype.map.call(selects, function (s) { return s.value; }).join(' / ');
      var variant = variantMap[key];
      if (variant) {
        hiddenInput.value = variant.id;
        if (btn) {
          btn.disabled = !variant.available;
          btn.textContent = variant.available ? 'Agregar al carrito' : 'Agotado';
        }
      }
    }

    selects.forEach(function (s) { s.addEventListener('change', updateVariant); });
    updateVariant();
  });
})();
</script>
